""" MOVEMENT
" Move between windows
map <c-j> <c-w>j
map <c-k> <c-w>k
map <c-l> <c-w>l
map <c-h> <c-w>h
noremap <Up> <NOP>
noremap <Down> <NOP>
noremap <Left> <NOP>
noremap <Right> <NOP>
map <A-C-Left>  :bprevious<CR>
map <A-C-Right> :bnext<CR>


